%   tricount     - count the number of triangles in an undirected unweighted graph
%   adj_to_edges - create an edge incidence matrix from an adjacency matrix
%   check_adj    - ensure A is a valid adjacency matrix
%   edges_to_adj - create an adjacency matrix from an edge incidence matrix
%   tri_matlab   - run tricount tests in MATLAB
%   kron_demo    - test Program/kron_demo.c and compare with MATLAB kron
%   kron_test    - test kron_demo.m
%   dpagerank    - compute the pagerank of nodes in a graph using a real semiring
%   ipagerank    - compute the pagerank of nodes in a graph using an integer semiring
%   rowscale     - row scale an adjacency matrix by out-degree

